query:
SELECT p.id, p.orderNumber, p.orderDate, p.invoiceDate, p.areaId, a.name as areaName, h.customerName as hospitalName
FROM purchases p
LEFT JOIN areas a ON p.areaId = a.id
LEFT JOIN hospitals h ON p.hospitalId = h.id
WHERE a.name LIKE '%Ward 33 North%'
ORDER BY p.orderDate DESC
LIMIT 10
